title: No, Kejriwal Chants Were Not Raised at India-Pak World Cup Match
subtitle: A video, shared by several users on Twitter, claims that slogans of ‘Kejriwal Jeetega’ were raised at the 2019 Cricket World Cup match that was played between India and Pakistan on 16 June, Sunday.
author: www.thequint.com
vclaim:
A video, shared by several users on Twitter, claims that slogans of 'Kejriwal Jeetega' (Translated: Kejriwal will win) were raised at the 2019 Cricket World Cup match between India and Pakistan in Manchester on 16 June, Sunday.
